{"tid":727521,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"好希望香港足波都有彈起一日","createTime":"2018-07-03T05:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T06:51:09.000Z","uid":45147,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6df9851b16f98427de69d737c5979aeef9a827ba","tid":727521,"uid":45147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:49:18.000Z","msg":"日本呢隊波勁在你睇下真係全隊架仔種族，香港整到又有白人又有力架都比人炒到癲<br />\n<br />\n唔好講入波嗰堆先，吉田6尺高身型削過lkk咁多幾乎頂佢頂足全場，唔係一早輸幾粒都似，其實打個比喻，香港既陳7同佢差唔多身材炸，點解人地隊波可以打到衝出國際，仲要有好幾個係啲得米七既典型毒撚身型都熱血到仆街又有腳法<br />\n<br />\n理論上我唔信成個亞洲得日本人得<br />\n<br />\n陣上既大迫當年打東亞運係輸比港隊，今年喺世界盃都有入波啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好想香港可以小說式咁抽一堆人離開呢個冇前途既地方發展下運動天份，十年廿年後幫手爭口氣，換黎冇高鐵坐又點話吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3029ed1e09e162aa1090a033e96d29e09d4b821d","tid":727521,"uid":21275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:52:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac76dce7b94c0ccf9cadfef3b56487abfc694530","tid":727521,"uid":45147,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3029ed1e09e162aa1090a033e96d29e09d4b821d","tid":727521,"uid":21275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:52:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"我意思係如果起膠鐵舊錢比左黎做呢樣野就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a